room_description: A cult has opened a portal to another dimension. They have kidnapped you to sacrifice to some unspeakable horror on the other side. You have 30 minutes before the creature reaches from beyond and devours you. Lucky for you, there are spirits of previous victims and a ritual to free them and yourselves. If you dare enter the portal, you and your party must gather clues and solve puzzles to escape your untimely fate.
